# Enforce LF for all text files in this plugin so content hashing is identical
# on Windows and Linux — the snapshot and fragment-determinism tests sha256
# LF-normalized output, and a Windows clone with core.autocrlf=true would
# otherwise get CRLF in the working tree and break byte-for-byte comparisons.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
